*   **Data-Hypothesis Mismatch**: The dataset is generated via a static two-factor linear model with GARCH(1,1) applied only to TSLA. There is no explicit mechanism for "volatility spillover" (e.g., VAR-GARCH or DCC-GARCH) in the data generating process. Any observed "topology" will be a mathematical artifact of the static factor loadings, not a reflection of underlying causal volatility transmission.
